---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — App Vitals"
  description="Meet Dan McAulay and Dave O'Dell — 40+ years of engineering leadership at Uber, Alto Pharmacy, and enterprise companies. Velocity engineering through AI adoption."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="glow-orb w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-accent-violet/[0.05] top-[-10%] right-[10%] animate-glow-drift" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-20 md:pt-32 md:pb-24 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="font-mono text-[13px] text-electric-400 tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-6 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up">
          About Us
        </p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.5rem)] font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.03em] opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up-delay-1">
          Move fast and build<br />
          things <span class="gradient-text">that last.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8 text-[18px] text-white/45 max-w-xl leading-[1.7] opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up-delay-2">
          Velocity engineers who accelerate the entire software development lifecycle — not just AI tool rollouts. We fix the pipeline, coach the people, and measure the results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="relative">
    <div class="gradient-divider"></div>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr,1.5fr] gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="font-mono text-[12px] text-electric-400 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Our Story</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem)] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.2]">
            Enterprise experience.<br />
            <span class="text-white/40">Startup intensity.</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-[16px] text-white/45 leading-[1.8] reveal" style="transition-delay: 150ms;">
          <p>
            We've spent 40+ combined years building and leading engineering teams at companies like Uber and Alto Pharmacy. We've navigated bureaucracy, shipped distributed systems for millions of users, and learned what it takes to move fast at scale.
          </p>
          <p>
            Now we're applying that experience to the biggest shift in software engineering since the cloud: AI-assisted development. Most teams know they should be using AI tools. Few know how to adopt them without creating a mess.
          </p>
          <p>
            That's the gap we fill. We don't roll out tools and hope for the best. We find the engineers who are already excited, coach them into champions, and help them spread adoption organically. Same bar for AI code as human code. No shortcuts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gradient-divider"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founders -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mb-16 reveal">
      <p class="font-mono text-[12px] text-electric-400 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">The Team</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem)] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em]">
        Two velocity engineers. Decades of depth.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Dan -->
      <div class="card-glow p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] reveal">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-8">
          <img src="/img/about/dan-profile.png" alt="Dan McAulay" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl object-cover" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-[22px] font-bold tracking-tight">Dan McAulay</h3>
            <p class="text-[13px] text-electric-400 font-mono tracking-[0.15em] uppercase">Co-Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-[15px] text-white/40 leading-[1.7]">
          <p>
            20+ years building at scale. Former engineering leader at Uber, where he worked on distributed systems serving millions of users. Deep expertise in platform engineering, team building, and navigating complex organizations.
          </p>
          <p>
            Dan brings the technical depth and organizational instinct that makes AI adoption work in practice — not just in demos.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Dave -->
      <div class="card-glow p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] reveal" style="transition-delay: 150ms;">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-8">
          <img src="/img/about/dave-profile.png" alt="Dave O'Dell" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl object-cover" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-[22px] font-bold tracking-tight">Dave O'Dell</h3>
            <p class="text-[13px] text-electric-400 font-mono tracking-[0.15em] uppercase">Co-Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-[15px] text-white/40 leading-[1.7]">
          <p>
            20+ years of engineering leadership across enterprise and healthcare companies, including Alto Pharmacy. Specializes in engineering velocity, developer experience, and building systems that scale.
          </p>
          <p>
            An AI-native practitioner who uses AI assistants daily to operate at startup velocity with enterprise quality. Hands-on expertise in making AI tools actually useful for real engineering work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="relative">
    <div class="gradient-divider"></div>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="mb-16 reveal">
        <p class="font-mono text-[12px] text-electric-400 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Our Approach</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem)] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em]">
          Principles, not playbooks.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-14">
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-1 h-6 rounded-full bg-electric-500"></div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight">Champions, not mandates</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-white/40 leading-[1.7] pl-5">
            Top-down AI mandates get ignored. We find the engineers who are already excited and help them become the proof that adoption works. Their peers follow because they see results — not because they were told to.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-1 h-6 rounded-full bg-accent-cyan"></div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight">Context is infrastructure</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-white/40 leading-[1.7] pl-5">
            AI tools are only as useful as the context they have. We build the foundation — architecture docs, shared patterns, conventions — that makes AI genuinely understand your codebase.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-1 h-6 rounded-full bg-accent-violet"></div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight">Ship first, strategize second</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-white/40 leading-[1.7] pl-5">
            We deliver production code in Week 1, not PowerPoints. Strategy comes from doing the work and seeing what actually moves the needle for your team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-1 h-6 rounded-full bg-electric-400"></div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight">Two founders + AI</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-white/40 leading-[1.7] pl-5">
            We're a small team by design. Two senior engineers leveraging AI tools means startup velocity with enterprise quality. No overhead, no layers, no diluted expertise.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="gradient-divider"></div>
    <div class="glow-orb w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-electric-500/[0.04] top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 animate-glow-drift" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 text-center relative z-10 reveal">
      <h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(1.75rem,4vw,3rem)] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.15]">
        Let's talk about <span class="gradient-text">your team.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-[17px] text-white/40 max-w-md mx-auto leading-[1.7]">
        30 minutes to understand where you are, where you want to be, and whether we're the right fit.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://cal.com/app-vitals-discovery"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center mt-10 px-10 py-4 bg-white text-navy-950 rounded-full text-[16px] font-semibold tracking-wide transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(59,130,246,0.3)] hover:scale-[1.02]"
      >
        Book a Discovery Call
        <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
